
# TSO Concepts and Commands


TSO
: Time sharing utility that allows users to send work to the processor. CPU takes the work and process small amounts before passing control to the next users

Without TSO all functions would have to be run in batch instead of real time

TSO allows dymamically allocating of 
* Lists
* Copy
* Delete 
* Rename


TSO allows for communication with JES2 or JES3 to submit background jiobs and progress can be monitored.

Standerd naming convention is Project.Group.Type
For example T74210.JCL.CNTRL(IEBCOPY)

Each qualifyer can be up to 8 charactres long and the total data set name lenght must not exceed 44 characters

